# testidea

- Install IntelliJ (IJ) with plugins La Clojure & Leiningen
- Install Leiningen
  - Download (https://raw.github.com/technomancy/leiningen/preview/bin/lein)
  - and run the lein script
- Configure Leiningen IJ plugin with above lein script
- lein new <yourproject> (command line)
- Create a new project in IJ from existing sources created by lein in previous step
- Open Leiningen tool window in IJ , "add Leining file", pick project.clj in <yourproject>
- Try out Leiningen goals in IJ for your project
- Done

## Usage

lein test

